    "Table 2 shows PF is over 2.5% better in test accuracy and balanced test accuracy, has higher AUROC and lower NLL.",
    "Hence, we take PF as best of the distance based category.",
    "Feature based classifiers are a popular recent theme.",
    "These extract descriptive statistics as features from time series to be used in classifiers.",
    "Typically, these features summarise the whole series, so we characterise these as series-to-vector transforms."
